---
import AboutHeroImage from '../assets/blog-placeholder-about.jpg';
import Layout from '../layouts/BlogPost.astro';
---

<Layout
	title="About Hosting Decoded"
	description="Learn more about Hosting Decoded and our mission to help Airbnb hosts succeed."
	pubDate={new Date('April 12 2026')}
	heroImage={AboutHeroImage}
>
	<p>
		Welcome to Hosting Decoded! We're dedicated to helping Airbnb hosts at every stage of their
		journey—from those just thinking about listing their first property to experienced hosts
		managing multiple rentals.
	</p>

	<p>
		The short-term rental industry has transformed how people travel and how property owners
		generate income. But with this opportunity comes complexity: pricing strategies, guest
		communication, local regulations, property management, and so much more.
	</p>

	<p>
		That's where we come in. Hosting Decoded breaks down the strategies and best practices
		that successful hosts use to maximize their earnings while providing exceptional guest
		experiences. We believe that with the right knowledge, anyone can become a successful host.
	</p>

	<h2>What We Cover</h2>

	<p>
		Our content spans everything you need to succeed as an Airbnb host:
	</p>

	<ul>
		<li><strong>Getting Started</strong> - Setting up your first listing for success</li>
		<li><strong>Pricing & Revenue</strong> - Dynamic pricing strategies to maximize earnings</li>
		<li><strong>Guest Experience</strong> - Creating stays that earn 5-star reviews</li>
		<li><strong>Operations</strong> - Streamlining cleaning, maintenance, and management</li>
		<li><strong>Growth</strong> - Scaling from one property to a portfolio</li>
	</ul>

	<p>
		Whether you're hosting a spare room or managing a vacation rental business, we've got
		insights to help you succeed.
	</p>
</Layout>
